name: Domenic J. IZZI et al. v. EMPLOYERS MUTUAL CASUALTY COMPANY et al.
name_abbreviation: Izzi v. Employers Mutual Casualty Co.

parties: Domenic J. IZZI et al. v. EMPLOYERS MUTUAL CASUALTY COMPANY et al.

opinions.text:
ORDER
The motion of plaintiffs and the motion of defendant Frank Lancia to affirm the judgment of the Superior Court pursuant to Rule 16(g) are denied.
DORIS, J., did not participate.

attorneys: Edmond A. DiSandro, Albert J. Lepore, Providence, for plaintiffs.

Domenic J. IZZI et al. v. EMPLOYERS MUTUAL CASUALTY COMPANY et al.

July 10, 1980.
Edmond A. DiSandro, Albert J. Lepore, Providence, for plaintiffs.
William Gerstenblatt, Providence, for defendants.
